CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 25, 2010

[Cite as 03/25/2010 Case Announcements #4, 2010-Ohio-1231.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2010-0499. [State ex rel.] Zukowski v. Brunner.

This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for an unspecified writ involving an expedited election matter. Upon consideration of relator’s urgent motion for hearing,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
